==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unseel
<hw>Un*seel"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>seel</ets>.]</ety> <def>To open, as the eyes of a
hawk that have been seeled; hence, to give light to; to enlighten.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

